## 🔑 Key Rules

**16 mandatory rules:** [EXECUTION/docs/ia/CANONICAL/rules/ia-rules.md](../../EXECUTION/docs/ia/CANONICAL/rules/ia-rules.md)

**Top 5 critical:**

1. Ports Mandatory — Use interfaces, not concrete implementations
2. Thread Isolation — Check execution-state/ for conflicts
3. Tests During Implementation — TDD, never test-after
4. No Implicit State — Verify everything before acting
5. Checkpoint After Work — Document what you implemented

